              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-300 animate-pulse"></span>
              <span class="text-cyan-200 text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold">Private-Parking Response · München & Bayern · 24/7 erreichbar</span>
            </div>
            <h1 id="hero-headline" class="text-[2rem] min-[390px]:text-[2.125rem] sm:text-5xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl 2xl:text-7xl font-black leading-[1.08] sm:leading-[1.04] tracking-[-0.035em] mb-4 sm:mb-5">
              Falschparker in München abschleppen lassen.
            </h1>
            <p id="hero-sub" class="text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-xl max-w-xl mb-5 sm:mb-6 leading-relaxed">
